data.description: HUGH PRICE REDUCTION. VA Assumable mortgage at 3.125% Fulton home is close to highly rated schools, a championship golf course, spring training MLB games, shopping, dining, & more!  5-bedroom 3 full bathroom home! Large living room w/ wood-look tile flooring in all the right places & a modern great room. The large eat-in kitchen has an abundance of on trend newer cabinets, updated countertops, updated backsplash & farm style sink.  The center island doubles as a breakfast bar & will seats up to 5. Guest bedroom, Full bathroom & laundry are down stairs!  Large main retreat has balcony access, a bathroom w/ dual sinks, and a walk-in closet. Backyard is an entertainers delight w/ a covered patio, pool w/ water features. New Pool pump, New Thermostate, & New Irrigation timer
